<br>
For those who are not aware, you gain more experience in the dungeons of Norrath (every zone has an experience multiplier).  <br>
<br>
While I do not think I will undertake to plan a &quot;formal&quot; raid, having no experience doing so....  If there is interest, perhaps we could get some planning done here on the board.  I am thinking that either tonight (Friday) or beginning early Saturday evening might be a good time.  <br>
<br>
Sammantha Thornheart<br>
Druidess of 20 Seasons<br>
